00:19:13.880 --> 00:19:16.320
<b>Ne?! Ben bir şey yapmadım!</b>  

00:19:16.320 --> 00:19:20.160
<b>Natsumi-san'ı ağlatan birine bırakamam.</b>  

00:19:20.160 --> 00:19:22.390
<b>Ben arkadaşın olacağım!</b>  

00:19:22.390 --> 00:19:25.280
<b>Kesinlikle. Natsumi'yi ağlatmamalısın!</b>  

00:19:25.280 --> 00:19:26.880
<b>Ben de onun arkadaşı olacağım.</b>  

00:19:26.880 --> 00:19:28.600
<b>B-Ben de!</b>  

00:19:28.600 --> 00:19:30.880
<b>Seni yanıma çırak alacağım. {I'm blanking on the appropriate word, but I think there's something better than kinsman that indicates being part a lower member of one's clan.}{TLC - This?}{apprentice can also work as well also retainer, but I think underling works best, trying to think of rikka-equese terms.}</b>  

